;; ai/flee, ai/flock, ai/flow-*, ai/follow-*, ai/grid, ai/max-force!,
;; ai/passable?, ai/path, ai/policy*, ai/pursue, ai/seek, ai/separate,
;; ai/utility, ai/wall!, ai/wander, ai/waypoints) belong to a
;; different lane — game-AI, not LLM-AI — and are already documented
;; in the reference. Some subset (ai/clear!, ai/decide, ai/flow-field,
;; ai/follow-flow, ai/follow-path, ai/grid, ai/policy, ai/wall!) are
;; ALSO returning auto-descriptors at src/wired-verbs.js:993-1001.
